Understanding columns in dataset

  1. total - number of drivers involve in collisions per billion miles
  2. speeding - percent of drivers involves in collisions due to speeding
  3. alcohol - percent of drivers involves in collisions due to alcohol intake
  4. not_distracted - percent of drivers involves in collisions who are not distracted
  5. no_previous - percent of drivers involves in collisions for first time
  6. ins_premiumn - premiumns for car
  7. ins_losses - loss for insurence companies
  8. abbrev - states
